BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:30d0f0c08701a3c7deca238de670a8b8@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260522T173247Z
DTSTART:20260523T130000Z
DTEND:20260523T135000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Drop-In/Pickup – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Basic Skills teaches the FUNdamentals of ice skating and provides the best foundation for figure skating\, hockey\, and speedskating.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Six progressive levels introduce forward and backward skating\, stops\, edges\, crossovers\, and turns:</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">&middot\; Basic 1 and 2 &ndash\; Discover\, Learn and Play: These introductory levels allow new skaters with no prior skating experience to build confidence while learning to skate.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">&middot\; Basic 3-6 &ndash\; FUNdamentals: These levels develop all of the fundamental skating skills on the ice. Focus is on learning the ABCs of basic athleticism: agility\, balance\, coordination and speed. </span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Upon completion of these levels\, skaters will be able to confidently advance to more specialized areas of skating. It is recommended that you complete two sessions of Snowplow Sam\, Pre-Hockey\, and/or Basic Skills (or masters gliding and stopping) prior to registering for Learn 2 Play Hockey.</span></p>\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
LOCATION:Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:686ef4aaac3edbcc50003f069c0253c0@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260522T173247Z
DTSTART:20260523T140000Z
DTEND:20260523T145000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Drop-In/Pickup – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:<p>The first stage of skills forms a strong foundation for your skaters to explore the world of skating. All will progress at their own pace working toward mastering each skill. Basic Skills will harness those skills as agility\, balance\, coordination and speed become the main focus of this curriculum. Basic Skills teaches the fundamentals of ice skating and provides the best foundation for figure skating\, hockey\, speedskating\, or recreation.</p>\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
LOCATION:Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:3b0fdc02b163bc80e6846ee246a1bea0@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260522T173247Z
DTSTART:20260523T140000Z
DTEND:20260523T145000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Drop-In/Pickup – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Basic Skills teaches the FUNdamentals of ice skating and provides the best foundation for figure skating\, hockey\, and speedskating.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Six progressive levels introduce forward and backward skating\, stops\, edges\, crossovers\, and turns:</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">&middot\; Basic 1 and 2 &ndash\; Discover\, Learn and Play: These introductory levels allow new skaters with no prior skating experience to build confidence while learning to skate.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">&middot\; Basic 3-6 &ndash\; FUNdamentals: These levels develop all of the fundamental skating skills on the ice. Focus is on learning the ABCs of basic athleticism: agility\, balance\, coordination and speed. </span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Upon completion of these levels\, skaters will be able to confidently advance to more specialized areas of skating. It is recommended that you complete two sessions of Snowplow Sam\, Pre-Hockey\, and/or Basic Skills (or masters gliding and stopping) prior to registering for Learn 2 Play Hockey.</span></p>\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
LOCATION:Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6f0d8a9e5a2d49e3fe7fceda4a5a92e2@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260522T173247Z
DTSTART:20260523T150000Z
DTEND:20260523T153000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Drop-In/Pickup – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">The Snowplow Sam levels are introductory classes divided into four progressive levels allowing children with no prior skating experience to build confidence while learning the basic skills of skating. These classes are designed to help children seven and younger develop the ABCs of movement &ndash\; Agility\, Balance\, Coordination and speed. The ABCs are essential for developing fundamental movement skills and physical literacy. All classes will be taught in a safe and positive environment\, incorporating fun and games making class time an enjoyable experience for all. It is recommended that you complete two sessions of Snowplow Sam\, Pre-Hockey\, and/or Basic Skills (or masters gliding and stopping) prior to registering for Learn 2 Play Hockey.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Off-ice orientation prior to the first skating class:</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">&middot\; Equipment check &ndash\; Proper fit and lacing of skates\, appropriate attire\, and safety helmets.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">&middot\; Practice falling and recovery\, marching in place\, dips and one-foot balances.</span></p>\n<p><span class="x-el x-el-span c1-7b c1-7c c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g">Students must pre-register online and each class is limited to 8 skaters. Classes may be combined or cancelled if enrollment numbers are below 3 skaters. Rental Skates included. BIKE OR HOCKEY HELMET REQUIRED. </span></p>\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
LOCATION:Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration
END:VEVENT
